- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with language processing systems and semantic relatedness of terms. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is also likely as the paper discusses language resources for evaluation of systems for computing semantic relatedness. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper mentions the use of a machine learning approach for generating the fifth language resource. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with the development of language resources for use in AI systems. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper may discuss the use of neural networks or evolutionary algorithms in the development of the language resources.
